==Indonesian==

===Adjective===
''bokep ''

(pornographic film) - originated from abbreviation BF which means Blue Film. BF is read Be-Ef, which in its pidgin form is read as Be-Ep. The word Bokep obtained by inserting ok in between Be-Ep.

===Verb===
''bokep''

to watch pornography.

====Transformation====
*'''ngebokep''': Active Intransitive Verb using affix '''me-V'''
